    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A classic isometric linear classless RPG. Wield the power of strength and the elements against threats to the worlds under your Canis Watch. Complete your Canis Watch alone or with others in unrestricted drop-in and drop-out progression.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Control The Powers Of Strength And Magic</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield the powers available to the Mawr during your Canis Watch. Strengths and magics classic to the natural world as well as unique feats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/022d730a751e0d8cfe88bc0d88acac72.poster.avif?t=1732218758\" width=180 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/022d730a751e0d8cfe88bc0d88acac72.webm?t=1732218758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/022d730a751e0d8cfe88bc0d88acac72.mp4?t=1732218758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/e28f4c6ae7ca1582cb8294db60b0e916.poster.avif?t=1732218758\" width=180 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/e28f4c6ae7ca1582cb8294db60b0e916.webm?t=1732218758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/e28f4c6ae7ca1582cb8294db60b0e916.mp4?t=1732218758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/3863aa66144233b40d1d3a4f7fd0d8bc.poster.avif?t=1732218758\" width=180 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/3863aa66144233b40d1d3a4f7fd0d8bc.webm?t=1732218758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/3863aa66144233b40d1d3a4f7fd0d8bc.mp4?t=1732218758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Visit Worlds With Their Own Stories</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel across landscapes familiar to wildlife of lush woods and arid lands alike. Uncover the oral histories and recent events which have the Canis Watch to thank. The adventure is not without adversity, but it is up to the Canis Watch to bring about a resolution. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/95cb0a555a8e422798ce3ddd9714c1fa.avif?t=1732218758\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/fe854f2826c5a9de8df15d46bae81b86.avif?t=1732218758\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/e444958bb59f11c83cf446895e37bba9.avif?t=1732218758\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/017d4d506f550f5b9fcf06d0e012ed34.avif?t=1732218758\" width=150 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Build Power By Finding And Combining Essences</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and loot essences of power throughout the worlds.<br>Buy and trade or upgrade to your needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267090/extras/a98b958d41436c56a5e7dc92af27fd70.avif?t=1732218758\" width=470 height=268 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Your Canis Watch</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Canis Watch has been assigned to you. Will you, Mawr, overcome your Canis Watch?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD Support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Camera Rotation (Yaw)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Searchable Inventories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Toggle Enemy Level Scaling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust Enemy Difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enable or Disable Friendly Fire</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peer-2-Peer Host List</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peer-2-Peer Password Protection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer Quest Sharing</p></li></ul>",
